Thank you for joining us at tonight's New York premiere of #ShowMeAHero, coming to #HBO this Sunday, August 16 at 8PM.
"He was a decent man that was caught up in the black hole that was politics in Yonkers at the time." - Daniel Sauli on playing Terry Zaleski
Daniel Sauli at the New York premiere for #ShowMeAHero
"This [racism] is right in New York, right in our backyard, and it's still happening." - John Salatin #ShowMeAHero
"What I have seen brings back so many memories and brings tears to my eyes." - Nay Noe Wasicsko #ShowMeAHero
"We all want somewhere decent we can call home, and we all deserve that" - @melnking #ShowMeAHero
"[#ShowMeAHero is] a reflection on where we are as a nation, which is nowhere when it comes to race" - Writer and Exec. Producer Bill Zorzi
Writer and Exec. Producer Bill Zorzi at the New York premiere for #ShowMeAHero
"It's a very American story. How do people who live here welcome new people?" - Peter Riegert #ShowMeAHero
"It's a difference between people have been forced to live and how they dream to live" - LaTanya Richardson Jackson
"We all want the same things - to provide for ourselves and our families in a safe environment." - @IlfeneshHadera
"Everyone loves a great story and these two men [@AoDespair + @Paul_Haggis] know how to tell a story." - @JimBelushi
"It talks about how everyone needs a place to call home. My character just wants that feeling of home" -Natalie Paul
"It shows politicians are trying to balance what's best for them and the people who voted for them." - @Domfishback
#ShowMeAHero actors Winona Ryder and Oscar Isaac at tonight's big New York premiere. Stay tuned for more.
"I'm such a huge [David Simon] fan and to be part in any way of one of his stories is a humbling experience." - Winona Ryder #ShowMeAHero
"It's great to entertain, but it's also great to be part of the argument." - Oscar Isaac #ShowMeAHero
"The story is that there are really two Americas. Why is that the case?" - Oscar Isaac #ShowMeAHero
"This is the type of story that's very current. It's happening right now." - @Paul_Haggis #ShowMeAHero
"There are many questions this series brings up that people need to be talking about" - Director & Exec. Producer @Paul_Haggis #ShowMeAHero
